originalText.text: I met Jeanette about seven yrs ago. I was introduced to her through a friend because I needed a resume. She was very patient and listened to everything I had to say as well as what type of position I was looking for. She is very articulate and knew exactly what I needed. I would recommend her highly to anyone that is looking to have their resume done.She is really great both as an individual and as a resume writer.

originalText.text: My resume needed a touch up after few years as I had not kept it up to date. I turned to Image Resume NYC to bring it up to the current standards and I was extremely satisfied with the result. Jeanette was responsive and got my resume looking more professional and ready for the current business world. I've sent it out to one place already and I already have the job offer in hand after the interview. I couldn't be happier with going with Image Resume NYC.
